articles.author: James Newbold
articles.title: Australian GP promoter found in rules breach after F1 track invasion - Motorsport.com
articles.description: The Australian Grand Prix promoter has been found in serious breach of FIA security protocols and safety measures after Formula 1 fans invaded the track before the race had ended.
